5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif&h=c118adaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會去維園"},{"pid":"551ffe6337b6b279f0a4318d39d60b69ea85649b","tid":2046182,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42ba318f942eefd0d61d3182fc3179189bfc23af","tid":2046182,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"笑到pk<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫毓民, 蟲泰, 鳩達 入維園<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"【🕯️遍地燭光悼六四 Candlelight in every corner of Hong Kong to mark June 4】<br />\n<br />\n📍各區64街站地點見圖。<br />\n請協助廣傳，謝謝！Please help to share, thank you.<br />\n<br />\n1．收看及分享🕯️「六四」31周年燭光悼念集會<br />\n📡 <a href=\"http://www.64live.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.64live.org&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=4aa7e5de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.64live.org</a><br />\n2．⏰ 8時正 無論你身處何地，一起燃亮燭光<br />\n3．⏰ 8時09分 默哀1分鐘<br />\n4．⏰ 8時30分 集會結束<br />\n5．將參與活動相片、感想加上標籤 #6431truth，上傳到個人 Facebook、Twitter、Instagram等社交媒體，以顯示香港人及全球的共同力量。瀏覽 #6431truth 標籤牆可到：<a href=\"https://walls.io/i5mvq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwalls.io%2Fi5mvq&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=9a66a702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://walls.io/i5mvq</a><br />\n<br />\n1. Watch 🕯️ the June 4 Candlelight Vigil 📡 live at <a href=\"http://64live.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F64live.org&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=0e51551c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://64live.org</a><br />\n2. ⏰ 8:00pm：no matter where you are, light candles together<br />\n3. ⏰ 8:09pm：one minute of silence<br />\n4. ⏰ 8:30pm：end of assembly<br />\n5. Photos and thoughts at #6431truth for Facebook, Twitter ,Instagram , to show the united strength of people in Hong Kong people and around the world. visit Tag Wall: <a href=\"https://walls.io/i5mvq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwalls.io%2Fi5mvq&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=9a66a702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://walls.io/i5mvq</a><br />\n<br />\n**尚有更多街站，請留意各自地區宣傳。街站或因天氣、突發情況變動，倘未能即時通知，請諒！感激所有團體友好、義工的幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【「六四」三十一周年燭光悼念網上集會程序 31st Anniversary of June 4 Candlelight Vigil &mdash;Online Assembly Program】<br />\n<br />\n下載 download：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/6431clv01．https://bit.ly/6431clv02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F6431clv01%EF%BC%8Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F6431clv02&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=174a01fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/6431clv01．https://bit.ly/6431clv02</a><br />\n<br />\n8:00：網上集會正式開始，市民燃點燭光<br />\n8:01：播放錄像「六四」31周年&mdash;&mdash;香港人由支援到抗爭<br />\n8:09：默哀一分鐘<br />\n8:10：播放「天安門母親」群體成員尤維潔錄像講話<br />\n8:16：齊唱《自由花》<br />\n8:21：誦讀《大會宣言》<br />\n8:25：齊唱《民主會戰勝歸來》<br />\n8:30：喊口號：<br />\n釋放民運人士！平反八九民運！追究屠城責任！結束一黨專政！建設民主中國！<br />\n五大綱領，抗爭到底！<br />\n反對國安法！反對以言入罪！<br />\n<br />\n8:00 pm：No matter where you are, light candles together<br />\n8:01 pm：Video &ndash; Hongkongers from support to our own fight<br />\n8:09 pm：One minute of silence<br />\n8:10 pm：Video &ndash; Speech of You Weijie, member of Tiananmen Mothers<br />\n8:16 pm：Song&ldquo;The Flowers of Freedom&rdquo;<br />\n8:21 pm：Manifesto of Hong Kong Alliance<br />\n8:25 pm：Song&ldquo;Democracy will triumphantly return&rdquo;<br />\n8:30 pm：Chanting of slogans：<br />\nRelease the Dissidents! Rectify the Verdict on the 1989 Movement! Demand Accountability for the Massacre! End One-Party Dictatorship! Build a Democratic China!<br />\nFive Platforms Fight till the end！<br />\nOppose National Security Law！<br />\nOppose Speech Crime！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;集會完成 End of assembly&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n📡 直播 LIVE：<a href=\"https://64live.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F64live.org&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e8b672f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://64live.org</a> ． <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/clv64hka\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fclv64hka&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=76051ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/clv64hka</a> ．<a href=\"https://www.fb.com/hka8964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fhka8964&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e915daaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fb.com/hka8964</a><br />\n<br />\n📑 網頁 online：<a href=\"https://64vigil.wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F64vigil.wordpress.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=9e6079b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://64vigil.wordpress.com</a> ．<a href=\"https://hka8964.wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhka8964.wordpress.com&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwI